  <div class="views-field views-field-field-explanation">        <div class="field-content"><br>"O king, the divine Sanatkumara had narrated a story about your posterity in the presence of sages.<br></div>  </div>  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd">
      
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content">à¤à¤¾à¤¶à¥à¤¯à¤ªà¤¸à¥à¤¯à¤¤à¥ à¤ªà¥à¤¤à¥à¤°à¥à¤½à¤¸à¥à¤¤à¤¿ à¤µà¤¿à¤­à¤£à¥à¤¡à¤ à¤à¤¤à¤¿ à¤¶à¥à¤°à¥à¤¤:à¥¤<br><br>à¤à¤·à¥à¤¯à¤¶à¥à¤à¥à¤ à¤à¤¤à¤¿ à¤à¥à¤¯à¤¾à¤¤à¤¸à¥à¤¤à¤¸à¥à¤¯ à¤ªà¥à¤¤à¥à¤°à¥ à¤­à¤µà¤¿à¤·à¥à¤¯à¤¤à¤¿à¥¤à¥¤1.9.3à¥¤à¥¤ <br><br></div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-htetrans">        <div class="field-content"><br>à¤à¤¾à¤¶à¥à¤¯à¤ªà¤¸à¥à¤¯ for Kasyapa, à¤µà¤¿à¤­à¤£à¥à¤¡à¤: à¤à¤¤à¤¿ named Vibhandaka, à¤¶à¥à¤°à¥à¤¤: famous, à¤ªà¥à¤¤à¥à¤°: à¤à¤¸à¥à¤¤à¤¿ has a son, à¤¤à¤¸à¥à¤¯ for him, à¤à¤·à¥à¤¯à¤¶à¥à¤à¥à¤ à¤à¤¤à¤¿ named Rsyasringa, à¤à¥à¤¯à¤¾à¤¤: wellknown, à¤ªà¥à¤¤à¥à¤°: son à¤­à¤µà¤¿à¤·à¥à¤¯à¤¤à¤¿ will be born.<br></div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-explanation">        <div class="field-content"><br>Kasyapa has a famous son named Vibhandaka. It was prophesied that he would have a son named Rsyasringa.<br></div>  </div>  </div>
